lad for $7.77. Oh, by the way the traffic in Las Vegas is unreal. At this resort they will ask you to take a 90 minute sales tour. It was the easiest $75 dollars I have ever made. No pressure at all. They show you the units and the cost and there is no pressure at all. If not interested just say no. Las Vegas is growing like you would not belive, and by the way the TRAFFIC IS TERRIBLE. My next vacation I am going somewhere there are no people and no traffic.	
